data.description: Now is your opportunity to own this gorgeous, "renovated" corner lot "block" home in the heart of Tampa! No HOA / No CDD property. This wonderful home features 3 beds and 2 baths have so much to offer. Home has newer flooring, newer kitchen, new paint inside/outside, and a newly fenced backyard for more privacy. You're just minutes away from Downtown Tampa, Ybor City, Tampa Bay's best award-winning restaurants and entertainment, and only a short drive away to Schools, Malls, Hospitals, 1-75, I-4 and beaches which ranked #4 in the Florida State Park list of the US's best beaches. It's just too much fun to list; come see for yourself. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make this beautiful property your home! Schedule your private showing today. OWNER MOTIVATED - ALL OFFERS WILL BE ENTERTAINED.
